cs.GT, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.MA 

This paper is about analyzing the dynamical properties of multi-agent strategic interactions, which is a topic in game theory. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.GT (Computer Science - Game Theory and Economics). The paper also discusses adaptive learning dynamics, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with convergence behavior, which is a topic in optimization (cs.SI) and multi-agent systems (cs.MA).
